    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="F204A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I'll tell you how the Sun rose -</l>
                    <l>A Ribbon at a time!  </l>
                    <l>The Steeples swam in Amethyst!  </l>
                    <l>The news like squirrels ran!  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The hills untied their Bonnets!</l>
                    <l>The Bobolinks begun!  </l>
                    <l>Then I said softly to myself </l>
                    <l>&quot;That must have been the sun&quot;!  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>But how he <em>set,</em> I know not!  </l>
                    <l>There seemed a purple stile</l>
                    <l>Which little yellow boys and girls </l>
                    <l>Were Climbing all the while - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Till when they reached the other side, </l>
                    <l>A Dominie in gray </l>
                    <l>Put gently up the evening bars</l>
                    <l>And led the flock away!  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
